Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:06.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,When Kogoro-no-occhan was hired to be \Nidol-singer Risa Purple's bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:09.11,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran and I were invited to her concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:14.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the concert, two men mistook \NRan for Risa and kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:20.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Then the old man and I pursued the kidnappers \Nand tracked down their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:24.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But there we saw plans for a kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,arranged by the kidnappers \Nand Risa Purple herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:31.58,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"Takeyama-san, please. Please save me."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:36.52,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Please take me from the stage \Non the day of the concert?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,"Pull the fire alarm and\Ncause a commotion?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a blueprint of the event space!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:48.90,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama responded fifteen minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:53.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"Risa-chan, we accidentally kidnapped \Nsome girl we don't recognize."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,"What should we do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.37,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If it was an accident, \Nthey should let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.71,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:08.40,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ran has seen their faces, it's \Nhard to imagine they'll let her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.82,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The less forethought someone has,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:13.39,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,the more capable they are of just about \Nanything when they feel cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.62,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that means taking someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:22.45,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A canvas stained black with crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:24.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,With brilliant detective \Nskills, its color is changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:26.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Ran has been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,How will they attempt to save her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:32.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.07,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:20.97,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(401,1)}Kogoro's Pursuit of Rage\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:19.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Kogoro's Pursuit of Rage, Part Two!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest Risa Purple immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:34.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,If she's the one who planned this \Nkidnapping, she must know where this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.77,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure is explaining the \Nsituation to Risa-san right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:40.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait! I'll get it out of her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.15,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's something funny \Nabout this Facenet picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.21,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:51.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,In her posters, the left side of her \Nface is always facing the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:57.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Risa Purple's most charming feature \Nis the mole under her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:01.85,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she always shows the left side \Nof her face in every picture she takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But this picture is taken \Nfrom her right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense for her \Nto upload a picture like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:12.26,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean someone was \Npretending to be Risa-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.67,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,and exchanging emails with Takeyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.24,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's an answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:26.62,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Takeyama's Facenet \Ndid say that he wanted her to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:32.37,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit pretending to be Risa-san may \Nbe planning to leave some kind of message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.00,DCItalic,ANSWERING MACHINE,0000,0000,0000,,I can't come to the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.86,DCItalic,ANSWERING MACHINE,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave a message after the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.77,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They're entering a security code.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:45.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit's trying to listen to \Ntheir messages from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.81,DCItalic,ANSWERING MACHINE,0000,0000,0000,,You have no new messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ran?! She'd better be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.02,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:05.90,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the culprit knows about \Nus, they probably won't call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:07.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.35,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.83,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man who chased \Nme out of the concert hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.25,Takichi,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Takeyama Takichi (43)\NRecycling Shop Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:19.25,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yosaburo! This happened because \Nof the mistake you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:24.13,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But, sir, unlike you, I'm not \Ninterested in Risa Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:24.05,Yosaburo,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Ihara Yosaburo (28)\NRecycling Shop Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.38,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know her face very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.88,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult Risa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:29.93,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:37.19,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,If we get caught, Risa-chan \Nwill get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.90,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. They won't find her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.81,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:57.99,DCItalic,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Conan-kun. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:05.34,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't use Facenet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:07.51,Risa,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Risa Purple (21)\NIdol
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.78,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And I didn't send those comments \Nor messages to my fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:12.14,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Someone must \Nbe pretending to be her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.02,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Risa is finally starting \Nto gain some popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.48,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She wouldn't gain anything from \Ncausing a commotion like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.81,Ginji,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\faqd(250,1)}Yamane Ginji (38)\NRisa's Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.81,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's nothing but trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:30.58,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's enough, you two. Stop filming this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:32.03,Junichi,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Sakuta Junichi (34)\NBeika Cable TV Director
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:34.66,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But everyone's following this news story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:38.16,Bianca,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fafd(250,1)}Bianca (26)\NConcert MC
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.16,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's the top news story online right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:44.92,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your cooperation, but don't \Nforget that the investigation is still ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:50.92,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,You still think one of us is \Nworking with the kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.34,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.35,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to confirm the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.48,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,If someone hadn't unlocked the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.48,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,the kidnappers wouldn't have been \Nable to pull the fire alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:08.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san, you said you went out into the \Nhallway just before the concert started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:15.85,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Like I said before, I just went to make \Na phone call. I didn't unlock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.40,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.84,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth were you calling \Nwhen you should've been busy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.38,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,with the concert that was about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.59,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.66,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.88,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide anything. Tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:36.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.14,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:45.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The manager was calling Takeyama, \None of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.32,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.20,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:55.20,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,We know who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.95,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave another threatening message, \Nyou won't get off with just a ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.88,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the shit out of you \Nand turn you over the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.96,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.21,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.58,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.47,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to be so rude toward my fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.97,DCMain,RISA,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked you so many \Ntimes to stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.86,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san, why did you have \NTakeyama's phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:27.65,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I saved his number when I received \None of his phone threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.38,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I didn't know it was Takeyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:36.87,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't stand the threat of violence \Nhe left just before a concert, so to be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:42.01,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anyone in the hallway \Nwhen you placed this call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.62,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:49.39,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see the fire \Nalarm from where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.63,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if anyone was there or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, violence is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.18,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to figure out \Nwhere that place in the photo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran is probably here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.15,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:16.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's somewhere Takeyama and his \Naccomplice were illegally dumping garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:20.91,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They threw away the refrigerator they \Ntrapped Ran-neechan inside there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.16,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We've determine the service area \Nthe kidnappers called from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.26,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The base station covers the area \Nfrom Beika Pass to Teimuzu Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.04,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty broad area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.74,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Have them search the area from the \Nskies with a helicopter immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.30,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.18,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But places that people are likely to \Nillegally dump garbage are hard to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:44.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'll be able to find it \Nby searching at night with a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:52.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And if the refrigerator is closed, she'll \Nrun out of oxygen in just a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran won't last until tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.53,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We have a search team\Nof 500 men ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:09.82,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,but they can't start until we \Nnarrow down the search area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.42,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.09,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send a message to the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them to spare Ran's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.31,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them the honest feelings \Nof their victim's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:32.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but appeal to \Nthe consciences of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:38.70,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but how \Non earth are you going to reach them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.87,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:49.46,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you broadcast my message to \Nthe kidnappers on your program?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.57,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,On our program?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:58.21,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but we're a cable channel. \NOur viewership is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:02.42,DCMain,SAKTUA,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlikely that your message \Nwill reach the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the odds are slim, we have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.85,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Just sitting and waiting \Nwon't save Ran's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.27,DCMain,SAKTUA,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. We'll start making \Npreparations immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.46,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.89,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-kun's life is on the \Nline. Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.53,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.67,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.80,Rainbow,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:53.91,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.07,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting soon. You should come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:01.57,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Risa-san was originally \Npart of a group, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.74,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At first there were seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:11.75,DCMain,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,They kept reforming their \Ngroup, but it never took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:20.12,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,We're live in three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.34,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm sure you all know already,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:30.81,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,today someone was kidnapped \Nfrom Risa Purple-san's concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:35.60,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! Risa \NPurple has been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:41.53,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,The video you're about to see is a message
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:46.03,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,from the father of kidnapping victim Mori \NRan-san, Mori Kogoro-san, to the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.34,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mori Kogoro, a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:13:00.04,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I know you mistook my daughter \Nfor Risa-san and kidnapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:04.22,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter surely has no value to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.93,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You may think she's just another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.68,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, my daughter is \Nan irreplaceable treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.48,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter is only 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:23.12,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Though she doesn't tell her father anything, \NI'm sure she dreams of a happy future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:29.24,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And you're trying to take that \Nfuture from her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.63,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter has done nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:35.12,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Please think calmly about this \Nand at least spare her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:39.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to become murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:47.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You may believe silencing my daughter will \Nallow you to escape, but you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:52.51,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have evidence of \Nthe real culprit's identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence of the real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:12.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Before the concert, my daughter took \Npictures all over the concert hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Among several of those photos,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:25.72,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,it's very likely that she took pictures of\Nsomeone standing where no one should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.09,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Of someone who shouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.35,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Not even I know who that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:38.54,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But this should be enough for you to \Nunderstand what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:44.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The true culprit should know \Nthose photos are solid evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:49.86,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,At dawn, the police will mobilize \Na 500 man search party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:53.87,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,They'll request assistance from the \Nfire department, mountain rescue,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.37,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and even the Self Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:15:00.78,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But if they discover the corpse of \Nmy daughter then, you'll be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:07.07,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be burdened with a \Ncrime you can never atone for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:11.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare my daughter \Nbefore it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That is my only request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.72,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,That was an impressive broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.40,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it reaches the \Nconsciences of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:31.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that it will, but if \Nthere's evidence on Ran's phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:35.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,they'll definitely act to destroy it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.98,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,He set a trap for the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.03,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:46.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoro-no-ojisan made up that Ran-neechan \Ntook pictures that could serve as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.99,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,He made it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:52.22,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dangerous gamble, but \Nit's the only way we can save Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:59.22,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Setting a trap is good and fine, but if the \Nreal culprit wasn't watching the broadcast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.19,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They were definitely watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.60,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.90,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, the real culprit is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.19,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:29.21,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know they were the real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,They left evidence on\Nthis answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.88,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.80,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The answering machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.56,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Will I get a bonus for this, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.32,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,You should be worrying about \NRisa-chan, not your bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.09,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming. Hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.21,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:14.05,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that ringtone \Nwas yours, Bianca-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:19.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,When the manager was leaving a \Nmessage on the answering machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,you could hear it very faintly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.94,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.94,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,We know who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.69,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave another threatening message, \Nyou won't get off with just a ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.60,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the shit out of you \Nand turn you over the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.45,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.44,DCItalic,YAMANE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:50.21,DCItalic,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca, what are you doing? \NIt's starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.41,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:56.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That was a phone call from the \Ndirector Sakuta-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:02.31,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. I was worried because we were \Nabout to start and I didn't see Bianca.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:09.24,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Risa-san with my life \Nno matter who dares to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.77,DCItalic,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,Bianca, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.44,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.63,DCItalic,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:18.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You did say something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.62,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta-san, did you know about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:30.26,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,No. Bianca said she might know where \NTakeyama's illegal dumping ground was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.68,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought we could get a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:36.34,DCMain,SAKUTA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the real culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.26,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.67,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yosaburo, let's run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.53,DCMain,IHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.64,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ran-neechan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.94,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.13,DCMain,TAKEYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,At the bottom of the pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:16.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.66,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:24.47,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.05,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.36,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.98,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.40,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.07,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Ran-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:43.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:48.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran... Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.63,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.33,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.18,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:02.63,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.39,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.96,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:15.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.90,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you're hurting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:18.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:28.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be wearing platform sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.01,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:34.18,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You knew the concert hall would be \Nfilled with water from the sprinklers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,so you wore shoes that wouldn't slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:42.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You've only ever worn platform sneakers \Nwhen you were an underground idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.34,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:51.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You were jealous that your \Njunior Risa-san became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:53.10,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:21:00.90,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if Risa was kidnapped, as the event\NMC, I would get attention and fame, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:08.84,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be easy to fool \NTakeyama since he came to all her events,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:12.29,DCMain,BIANCA,0000,0000,0000,,but things didn't go so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.31,DCNote,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.30,DCItalic,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mori Kogoro, a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:51.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're feeling better, Ran-neechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:53.36,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.56,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Even Shinichi was so worried he called \Nme while I was in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:00.31,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:06.32,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I didn't think you \Nloved me this much, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:09.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are they going to show that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:13.59,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,But your eyes are so red.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:16.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some impressive acting chops.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:17.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:21.17,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what you might think, I was \Nan aspiring actor when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.38,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Acting? You were acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:27.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:29.67,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You brat, why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:32.93,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Dad. Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:36.43,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! I have so many things to do today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.35,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:40.30,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Dad!
